Merb Words

Merb Publishing for Your Words

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To see all available tasks for Merb Words run:

rake -T slices:merb_words

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Instructions for installation:

file: config/dependencies.rb

# add the slice as a regular dependency

dependency 'merb-words'

# optionally configure the plugins in a before_app_loads callback

Merb::BootLoader.before_app_loads do

  Merb::Slices::config[:merb_words][:option] = value

end

file: config/router.rb

# add the slice

slice(:merb_words)

# run the following rake task:

rake slices:merb_words:install

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You can put your application-level overrides in:

host-app/slices/merb-words/app - controllers, models, views ...

Templates are located in this order:

1. host-app/slices/merb-words/app/views/*
2. gems/merb-words/app/views/*
3. host-app/app/views/*